		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Katyn massacre</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">"Katyn" and "Katyń" redirect here. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Katyn_(disambiguation)" title="Katyn (disambiguation)">Katyn (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">This article is about the 1940 massacre of Polish officers.  For the 1943 massacre of the Belarusian village, see <a href="/wiki/Khatyn_massacre" title="Khatyn massacre">Khatyn massacre</a>.</div>
